snippet.title: Hotline Miami Collection - Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Hotline Miami Collection contains both legendary games in the neon-soaked, brutally-challenging Hotline Miami series from Dennaton Games and Devolver Digital. Available today on Nintendo Switch!
